          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Low Drug Prices Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to establish maximum prices for prescription drugs that are covered under specified federal programs (e.g., Medicare) based on drug prices in listed reference countries.</p>]]></text>
